{"thig5.9:0.1":"Therigatha 5.9 ","thig5.9:0.2":"Pancakanipata ","thig5.9:0.3":"Bhaddakundalakesatherigatha ","thig5.9:1.1":"“Lunakesi pankadhari, ","thig5.9:1.2":"ekasati pure carim; ","thig5.9:1.3":"Avajje vajjamatini, ","thig5.9:1.4":"vajje cavajjadassini. ","thig5.9:2.1":"Divavihara nikkhamma, ","thig5.9:2.2":"gijjhakutamhi pabbate; ","thig5.9:2.3":"Addasam virajam buddham, ","thig5.9:2.4":"bhikkhusanghapurakkhatam. ","thig5.9:3.1":"Nihacca janum vanditva, ","thig5.9:3.2":"sammukha anjalim akam; ","thig5.9:3.3":"‘Ehi bhadde’ti mam avaca, ","thig5.9:3.4":"sa me asupasampada. ","thig5.9:4.1":"Cinna anga ca magadha, ","thig5.9:4.2":"vajji kasi ca kosala; ","thig5.9:4.3":"Anana pannasa vassani, ","thig5.9:4.4":"ratthapindam abhunjaham. ","thig5.9:5.1":"Punnam vata pasavi bahum, ","thig5.9:5.2":"Sappanno vatayam upasako; ","thig5.9:5.3":"Yo bhaddaya civaram adasi, ","thig5.9:5.4":"Vippamuttaya sabbaganthehi”ti. ","thig5.9:6.1":"… Bhadda kundalakesa theri …. "}